OL,3,CHealth watchdog 'not fit for purpose'
OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,7,Fsaid that England's health and social
OL,8,Fcare watchdog is "not fit for purpose"
OL,9,Fas he pledged immediate action to
OL,10,Frestore public confidence.
OL,12,FHis comments come after an independent
OL,13,Freview into the Care Quality
OL,14,FCommission (CQC), a body that monitors
OL,15,Fall health and adult social care
OL,16,Fproviders to ensure standards and
OL,17,Fsafety.
