OL,3,CHealth watchdog 'not fit for purpose'
OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FSome had said they had never been in a
OL,7,Fhospital prior to conducting an
OL,8,Fassessment and one inspector of a care
OL,9,Fhome stated they had never met someone
OL,10,Fwith dementia.
OL,12,FThe report found inspection numbers
OL,13,Fwere still well below pre-Covid
OL,14,Flevels, a lack of consistency in the
OL,15,Fwatchdog's assessments and issues with
OL,16,Fits IT system.
OL,18,FMr Streeting said: "When I joined the
OL,19,Fdepartment, it was already clear that
OL,20,Fthe NHS was broken and the social care
OL,21,Fsystem in crisis.
