OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,F"But I have been stunned by the extent
OL,7,Fof the failings of the institution
OL,8,Fthat is supposed to identify and act
OL,9,Fon failings. It's clear to me the CQC
OL,10,Fis not fit for purpose.
OL,12,F"We cannot wait to act on these
OL,13,Ffindings, so I have ordered the
OL,14,Fpublication of this interim report so
OL,15,Faction can begin immediately to
OL,16,Fimprove regulation and ensure
OL,17,Ftransparency for patients.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
