OL,6,FKate Terroni, CQC's interim chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "We accept in full
OL,8,Fthe findings and recommendations in
OL,9,Fthis interim review, which identifies
OL,10,Fclear areas where improvement is
OL,11,Furgently needed.
OL,13,F"Many of these align with areas we
OL,14,Fhave prioritised as part of our work
OL,15,Fto restore trust with the public and
OL,16,Fproviders by listening better, working
OL,17,Ftogether more collaboratively and
OL,18,Fbeing honest about what we've got
OL,19,Fwrong.
